===Noun===
{{wikipedia|Harrow (tool)}}
{{en-noun}}

#(farm implement) A device, pulled by a tractor, with several disks or teeth in a row to smooth or break up soil, typically after plowing, or to remove weeds or cover seeds; a harrow [[plow]].

